## Terraform Infra

```bash
cd terraform
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply  # Creates GCS crypto_project1-crypto-data, BQ dataset crypto_project1, SA + key at ../keys/gcp-credentials.json
```

Update `ingestion/upload_gcs/upload.py` bucket_name = "crypto_project1-crypto-data"

GCS path: gs://crypto_project1-crypto-data/parquet/year={year}/...
